snippet.title: Jermle | Free Game Release Trailer (2024)
snippet.description:
Play now in your browser: https://worblir.itch.io/jermle
It's what everybody's been waiting for!

A word guessing game where you can guess the word "Jerma".

Trailer music by @savestatecorrupted and @foxwithguns 

Part of the extended "Jerma's Big Adventure 2" ​universe. Wishlist now to support it (it'll be free!): http://store.steampowered.com/app/2227100
(and yes I am still developing Jerma's Big Adventure 2 and no more side stuff like this, I get a wee bit carried away)

Here's other links for me: https://linktr.ee/worblir

Disclaimer: This is a fan game and is unaffiliated with streamer funny-man Jerma985
